      "raw_text": "Charged with distributing liter\nature without a License, George\nSeaman and Soren Sorenson, two\nmembers of the l. w. w. army,\nwere arrested yesterday afternoon\nby Officer Cox. The prisoners were\nhanding out cards which announced\na meeting of February %, evidently\nalready held. The cards were ar\nranged to advertise an address by\nJames P. Thompson, an I. w. w.\n\"conspirator.\" now out of jail on\n$4,000 bonds. The prisoners were\nlocked up in default of bail."
    }
